CORRECTED-TO.","Ship a reusable, UNLABELED finding sample (~300 surfaced + ~100 dropped, floor ≥280/≥90) built by positional coverage.counts bucketing, excluding text-less findings.","The finding-adjudication TP/FP labeling was invalidated because the LLM raters were plan-truncated (PLAN_CAP=6000) and tool-less, contaminating 79% of labels versus production's whole-plan agentic grounding.","Human adjudication of the 30 disputes is also invalidated, since disputes were selected by the faulty A/B process and the human was anchored on truncated rater rationales without code grounding.","Finding-level TP/FP labeling is descoped to idea e59d-c078-724d-46e5; kappa/validity artifacts and disputes are not shipped, and the README records the invalidation rationale."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784253959399091001,"uuid":"601933d0-c97c-48de-9b90-c868f58eec23"}